quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  106,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  106,1,Quresh ke manoos karne ke sabab
  106,2,( yani ) un ko jaray aur garmi ke safar se manoos karne ke sabab
  106,3,logon ko chahiye ke ( is Nemat ke shukar mein ) is ghar ke maalik ki ibadat karen
  106,4,jis ne un ko bhook mein khana khilaya aur khauf se aman bakhsha
